{
  "stem": "25423.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was one guest, was a very strange man because he was always, on Fridays, invited to the rabbi's house, traditionally.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So as there were two chief rabbis who shared the rabbinical chairs, one Friday night he spent with one family, and one Friday night was another one.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His name was Senator Bodek Jakub Bodek.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was a senator.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was elected senator, representing the Jewish community in the Polish [INAUDIBLE], or senate, which is the equivalent of the Congress.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was the director of the railroad district for the Austro-Hungarian government.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was engaged to a young lady who died very shortly before the wedding.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the man dedicated his life to charity.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And all his life, he remained single, and just simply addressed himself to servicing the poor, the people in need.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And therefore, traditionally, the rabbis greeted him on Friday.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was always a guest, either at my father's home or the other rabbi.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, the housekeeper.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother was too busy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] That is my mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, I have to stress that my father was an orthodox rabbi.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And consequently, all the [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] restrictions and way of life which you would find in any Jewish orthodox home were present in my home.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No question about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The restrictions of kashrut and things like that didn't bother me too much.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just had to behave in-- in a way, in a fashion that people wouldn't come to my father saying that I'm behaving like a Gentile child, and get into fights and things of that sort.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What do you mean by that?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Position of the rabbi in the Old World was entirely different than it is here in the United States.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These people were law-givers.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
